01:39:21,000 --> 01:39:24,309
Change does not role in on the wheels..

01:39:24,559 --> 01:39:25,440
.. of inevitability.

01:39:25,390 --> 01:39:27,700
It comes through continous struggle.

01:39:30,026 --> 01:39:31,690
