01:39:32,000 --> 01:39:33,900
and I am dedicated to making sure...

01:39:34,095 --> 01:39:35,936
... his magic doesn't end with his death.

01:39:36,186 --> 01:39:37,664
He believed that he could change the world.

01:39:37,914 --> 01:39:39,498
And he was right.

01:39:39,748 --> 01:39:42,549
Out of the last week, and out of today..

01:39:42,799 --> 01:39:44,832
.. phoenixes are already rising.

01:39:47,220 --> 01:39:49,141
