01:39:48,693 --> 01:39:51,637
.. Rep. Zoe Lofgren and Sen. Ron Wyden..

01:39:51,887 --> 01:39:53,536
have introduced legislations that would reform

01:39:53,786 --> 01:39:55,370
... the Computer Fraud and Abuse Act.

01:39:55,620 --> 01:39:58,741
The outdated law that formed the majority of the charges..

01:39:58,991 --> 01:39:59,936
against Swartz.

01:40:00,186 --> 01:40:02,389
It's called "Aaron's Law."

01:40:02,639 --> 01:40:05,802
Aaron believed that like you literally ought to..

01:40:06,052 --> 01:40:07,424
.. be asking yourself all the time..

01:40:07,674 --> 01:40:11,157
.. "what is the most thing i could be working on in the world right now?"

01:40:11,407 --> 01:40:13,269
And if you are not working on that, why aren't you?

01:40:33,700 --> 01:40:37,098
I wish we could change the past, but we cannot.

01:40:37,348 --> 01:40:43,605
